  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Mobile Cacao and Grafting Technology for Cacao Producers in El Salvador</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project aims to strengthen cacao production through the following activities: 1) To complete 100 Training of Trainers courses for cacao producers in the grafting techniques, to expand coverage and increase the number of plants grafted 2) To strengthen the implementation of technology in agroforestry systems with cocoa: a) Establishment of 8 demonstration plots in strategic places to share technology between beneficiary and non-beneficiary producers b) Support with mobile technologies through Cacao M&#xF3;vil, and c) Preparation of a video on grafting.</narrative>
  </description>
